Class MethodRefactorabilitySettings

java.lang.Object
ac.code.verifier.configuration.MethodRefactorabilitySettings
public class MethodRefactorabilitySettings extends Object
The class MethodRefactorabilitySettings stores the settings of ExtractableMethod annotation.
